{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"225014-makurir-puwali","title":"মেকুৰীৰ পোৱালী","description":"এটা মেকুৰীৰ পোৱালীয়ে ঠেঙত দুখ পাইছিল। কোনোবাই তাক সহায় কৰিবনে?","language":"Assamese","langCode":"as","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Gayatry Borah"],"illustrators":["Partho Sengupta"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Pratham Education Foundation","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/225014-makurir-puwali"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/283164/size3/b9809682af44499c09b4e93c69d6e8e6.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/283164/size6/b9809682af44499c09b4e93c69d6e8e6.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/279127/size6/643a4e3399db2700ddf1cf94615f400f.jpg","text":"ৰীমাই\nঘৰৰ বাহিৰত খেলি আছিল।","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/279128/size6/78b2ac60c1d7368a848f657858e138c8.jpg","text":"তেতিয়া তাই কাৰোবাৰ কেকাই থকা মাত শুনিলে। \nতাই ইফালে-সিফালে চাব ধৰিলে।","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/279129/size6/93c586ed99970b86eea3f4dc0a5f5416.jpg","text":"এটা\nসৰু মেকুৰী পোৱালী ৰাস্তাৰ কাষত পৰি আছিল।","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/279130/size6/15b91647bf992326eea005f90c5e6ea8.jpg","text":"ৰীমা তাৰ ওচৰলৈ গ'ল।মেকুৰীটোৱে ঠেঙত\nদুখ পাইছিল।\nসেইটো দেখি ৰীমাই ভয় খালে।","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/279131/size6/065bc602849c315da6b14234f172eed0.jpg","text":"তাই মাকক মাতিলে।\nমাক বাহিৰলৈ আহিলে আৰু মেকুৰী\nপোৱালীটো ডাঙি ঘৰলৈ লৈ গ'ল।","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/279132/size6/2682fe98537a9436d81fa6ae12876bca.jpg","text":"মাকে মেকুৰীটোৰ ভৰিত দৰৱ লগাই কাপোৰেৰে বান্ধি দিলে।","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/279133/size6/bf71ae1d57bd4e19bbb1c8487327150e.jpg","text":"ৰীমাই এটা বাটিত অলপ গাখীৰ লৈ আনিলে।মাকে বাতিটো হাতত লৈ তাক গাখীৰ\nখুৱালে।\nগাখীৰ খাই সি মাকৰ কোলাত শুই গ'ল।","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/279134/size6/f2418ddeabdf2cce18b1adc9033ff6af.jpg","text":"সেইদিনাৰ পৰা মেকুৰী পোৱালীটো ৰীমাৰ লগত থাকিবলৈ ল'লে।","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":8,"words":85}}